<HEADLINE>
FT  04 MAY 94 / Cory Environmental: Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Our use of a photograph of the Cory Environmental Pollution Services site at
Mucking, Essex, to illustrate last Saturday's report on the introduction of
new rules for the waste disposal industry does not imply that Cory is
deficient, and it continues to operate under its existing licence as it
meets the new rules. We apologise for any embarrassment caused by the use of
the picture.
</TEXT>
